<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8">

<title>Happy 1 Month Anniversary ❤️</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Great+Vibes&family=Poppins:wght@300;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>

body{
background:#FFD1DC; /* pale pink */
font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
text-align:center;
color:white;
overflow:hidden;
}

.container{
margin-top:80px;
position:relative;
z-index:2;
}

h1{
font-size:45px;
font-family:'Great Vibes',cursive;
}

h2{
font-size:35px;
color:#ff2e63;
text-shadow:0 0 10px white,0 0 20px white;
}

p{
font-size:20px;
width:70%;
margin:auto;
}

button{
padding:12px 25px;
font-size:18px;
border:none;
border-radius:20px;
background:white;
color:#ff4b6e;
cursor:pointer;
margin-top:30px;
}

.hidden{
display:none;
margin-top:20px;
font-size:22px;
}

/* falling animation */

@keyframes fall{
to{
transform:translateY(100vh);
opacity:0;
}
}

.fall{
position:fixed;
top:-20px;
animation:fall linear;
z-index:1;
}

</style>
</head>

<body>

<audio autoplay loop>
<source src="song.mp3" type="audio/mpeg">
</audio>

<div class="container">

<h1>Happy 1 Monthhhh Anniversaryyyyyyyyyyyyy 💕🧿</h1>

<h2>Kushu ❤️ Tanu</h2>

<img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/40/Rose_flower.jpg/320px-Rose_flower.jpg" width="200">

<p>
its alrewdsyy 1 monthhhhh. and so much more to goo.... i lovee u so muchhhh....💗
</p>

<button onclick="showMessage()">Click this if you miss me 💌</button>

<div class="hidden" id="message">

kushhuuuuu.... i know its only been 1 month still we have seen fights and cries 💕  
but one thing is sure we are not gonna leave each other 🧿  
i can see our potential... what we are and what we can become 😘  
even if times are hard right now i'm always with you 🫂💕

</div>

<p style="margin-top:40px">
yourssss,<br>
<b>Tanu 🤭😚</b>
</p>

</div>

<script>

function showMessage(){
document.getElementById("message").style.display="block";
}

/* falling hearts & roses */

function createFall(){
const item=document.createElement("div");

item.innerHTML=Math.random()>0.5 ? "🌹":"❤️";

item.classList.add("fall");

item.style.left=Math.random()*window.innerWidth+"px";
item.style.fontSize=(20+Math.random()*30)+"px";
item.style.animationDuration=(4+Math.random()*4)+"s";

document.body.appendChild(item);

setTimeout(()=>{
item.remove();
},8000);
}

setInterval(createFall,300);

</script>

</body>
</html>
